metadata.name: Cosmic Girls #0001
metadata.description:
This is the profile of the crew who completed the training course to board the ship Noah.


Cosmic Voyager's training process is to communicate smoothly with various civilizations and intelligent bodies to be encountered,


It was evaluated with an emphasis on the attitude of accepting novelty.


The Cosmic Voyagers aboard Noah have a deep insight and understanding of various cultural contents,


It has various values, appearances, and music tastes.


The seat next to the colleague who will help you sail is empty.


Choose a colleague who will join you on the great voyage!
